# Drive purposes (strict)

| Drive | Purpose |
|-------|---------|
| `C:` | OS and tools only — not an app env |
| `E:` | **DEV** — default agent/development work |
| `F:` | **PREPROD** — staging runtime only |
| `G:` | **PROD** — production-like runtime only |
| `H:` | **RELEASES** — last 3 release packages only |

- Do not mix roles across drives.
- Default all coding work to `E:`.
- Touch `F:` / `G:` / `H:` only when the user names that environment.
- Release retention on `H:\releases\`: keep maximum 3; deleting older releases still requires user confirmation.
- Full standing orders: `workflow/CONSCIOUS.md`
